overview: An invitation to record with The Legendary Stardust Cowboy prompts Country  Willie Edwards and his band “The Cosmic Debris” to launch their first West Coast  tour. Having never broken the gravitational pull of Deep East Texas, six men, two  roosters, and one bus embark on a perilous journey to the other side of a dream.
tagline: Six men, two roosters, and a dream.
title: Rainbows End
